        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Patriot Retention Act</b></p> <p>This bill allows a retired service member who has more than 20 years of service, and who possesses a skill for which a critical shortage exists, to serve as a paid member of the Ready Reserve of the Armed Forces and concurrently receive retired pay.</p>]]>
        </text>
